title: PUBLIC NOTICE Crown Castle is proposing to install
text:
PUBLIC NOTICE Crown Castle is proposing to install ad date: 10/10/2015 
PUBLIC NOTICE Crown Castle is proposing to install antennas and replace the current tower at the following site: #857625 Hunter Creek located off of 11th Street in Gold Beach, Curry Co. - lat: 42-23-47.8 long: 124-24-47.63. Crown Castle invites comments from any interested party that believes the proposed action may have a significant impact on the environment or on any districts, sites, buildings, structures or objects significant in American history, archaeology, engineering or culture that are listed or determined eligible for listing in the National Register of Historic Places and/or specific reason the proposed action may have a significant impact on the quality of the human environment. Specific information regarding the project is available by calling Monica Gambino at 724-416-2516, during normal business hours. Comments must be received at Crown Castle USA - 2000 Corporate Drive, Canonsburg, PA 15317 attn Legal Dept. by October 16, 2015 Publish October 10, 2015
